          "value": "### **üî• We lost everything. But not our fire.**\n\nIn the off-season, someone broke into our shipping container in Alversj√∂ and emptied it.¬†\n\n*   We got back two sofas, two chairs, a lamp, 14 carpets, a couple other small items‚Äîthey were given to someone who returned them as soon as they worked out that they were ours‚Äîbut it‚Äôs a drop in the ocean and everything else is gone‚Ä¶ we do not expect to get anything more back.¬†\n    \n*   This dream grant is about moving forward, so please do not comment about the container situation here. If you have any questions, we‚Äôll be more than happy to answer them in private.\n    \n\n**üíî**I**n summary: we‚Äôre heartbroken and broke, but not broken!**\n\nThe Foxhole was already a lot of work for only 30 of us‚Äîand now it's daunting to think about rebuilding everything from nothing, but we are motivated! We‚Äôre a strong community and we dream that the Foxhole _will_ rise again **if you help us bounce back**!\n\n### **üî• What _is_ the Foxhole?**\n\nFor the uninitiated: imagine a sex-positive red velvet jazz lounge, dipped in candlelight, buzzing with connection. A dreamy blend of playroom, art gallery, dancefloor, and foxy mischief.\n\nWe‚Äôre a community that care deeply about creating beautiful, intentional experiences. We do it with mischief, yes‚Äîbut also with **respect, warmth, and heart.**\n\n**üíù This year, we‚Äôre putting even more love into every detail.**\n\n¬†More thoughtful programming. More sensory delight. More space to rest, explore, flirt, or simply feel at home. Everything from our structure to our colour palette is designed to **invite presence, pleasure, and play** in whatever way feels good for each guest.\n\n**Expect:**\n\n*   A richly furnished, layered environment that deepens as you move through it\n    \n*   A beautifully sensual and consensual playroom, where safety meets fantasy and lust\n    \n*   Events designed to spark meaningful connection and open-ended exploration\n    \n*   The most immersive sound system (without the sonic assault)\n    \n*   The best cocktails and alcohol-free elixirs in Borderland. See our other dream for details\n    \n\n### **üõ†Ô∏è Here‚Äôs the comeback plan:**\n\n1.  **Infrastructure rebuild** We need to replace all the infrastructure that we lost from the container: internal walls, DJ booth, stage, seating, podiums, fabrics, electrics, lights, trolleys, tools, ladders, etc. We are asking for donations of some larger items like fridges and freezers.\n    \n2.  **Interior redesign** Think velvet. Think Persian carpets. Think candlelit artwork and shadowy nooks that invite intimacy. We‚Äôll try to source **almost all interior design items through donations**: lamps, furniture, decor items, & 50% of the carpets we need. Please reach out if you can help us.\n    \n3.  **Queue** Last year, people waited _hours_ to get in. That‚Äôs how good it was. This year, we will focus on having shorter queues, and turning the queue into part of the experience. Do you have an interactive installation? Living sculptures? Piano project? Come collaborate with us.\n    \n4.  **Perfect sound all week** Crystal-clear, immersive, sexy AF. And, thanks to foxy friends, we only pay for two days of rental.\n    \n5.  **Kitchen, LNT & private gear** Sadly not covered by Dream Grants‚Äîbut we‚Äôre collecting donations. Got a fridge? A stove? Gas Burner? Slide into our DMs.\n    \n\n### **üíã Why it‚Äôs worth it**\n\nThis isn‚Äôt just about replacing what was lost. It‚Äôs about rebirthing something iconic. **Foxhole is a community of dreamers, doers, artists, DJs, lovers, and builders**. We‚Äôve created magic before (Photos from are Foxhole 2024), and we‚Äôll do it again‚Äîwith your help. Should more of our stuff appear, we‚Äôll reduce the dream grant accordingly.¬†\n\nWe‚Äôre not begging. We‚Äôre inviting. To rebuild something unforgettable. To co-create the most immersive, deliciously designed, and wildly welcoming space at Borderland 2025.\n\n**Bring the fangs‚Äîwe‚Äôll bring the feathers.** Let‚Äôs make this comeback legendary. ü¶äüíÑüõ†Ô∏è\n\n### **üíù Our other dreams**\n\n[Foxtent](https://cobudget.com/borderland/borderland-dreams-2025/cm8xheh4f104260cl1qw7lb2ai) -- [Foxy Fluids](https://cobudget.com/borderland/borderland-dreams-2025/cm8xcycda29810cic5bkb35g2)",
