          "value": "### **üéÅ What Is the Gift?**\n\nThis is a journey of falling ‚Äî into mystery, absurdity, and maybe even yourself._A-Hole Project_ is a scattered series of themed **infinity mirrors**, each one transformed into a different ‚Äúhole‚Äù:\n\n*   üåå **Black Hole**\n    \n*   üå™Ô∏è **Wormhole**\n    \n*   üê∞**Rabbit Hole**\n    \n*   üåø **Pot Hole**\n    \n*   üç© **Donut Hole**\n    \n*   üóùÔ∏è **Key Hole**\n    \n*   üß† **K-Hole**\n    \n*   üí© **Shithole**\n    \n\nAnd more... Each one is hidden somewhere around Borderland. You discover them like Easter eggs ‚Äî stumble upon a shimmering mirror in the woods, peer in, and fall into the illusion.\n\nIt‚Äôs a **magical-meets-absurd scavenger hunt**, a portal gallery, a constellation of strange beauty scattered across the landscape.\n\n### **üåà Why Fund This?**\n\nBecause Borderland thrives on \\*\\*mystery, play, and beauty hiding in absurdity.\\*\\*Because a scavenger hunt of portals into cheeky, cosmic, and chaotic experiences is exactly the kind of weird gift that makes people talk, laugh, reflect, and remember.\n\n_A Hole Project_ is immersive. It‚Äôs interactive. It‚Äôs deeply unserious ‚Äî and also a sincere exploration of what it means to fall‚Ä¶ into A Hole lotta crazy.\n\nInto darkness. Into pleasure. Into yourself. Into the stupidest pun you've ever seen.\n\n**üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è**\n\nGoal is to borrow/thrift as many materials possible. We have a push for using reusable items/ turning **trash into treasure** to make these art installations one of a kind! _No Temu Here!_\n\n**Sydhavn Genbrugscenter** is a great place for free wood/paneling and will be our first stop!\n\nThrough donations and scavenging, we‚Äôve already sourced core structural elements ‚Äî including **upcycled metal tubing and basic tools**. We may even have a possibility for a donation of 2-way mirror film.\n\nAll funds requested will go directly to lighting, mirror material, themed d√©cor, and bringing these portals to the NEXT LEVEL.\n\n**THE MORE YOU FUND THE MORE HOLES WE CAN FILL!!!**\n\n**üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è‚ú®üï≥Ô∏è**\n\nSo go ahead. Crawl out of a black hole. Stick your face in a wormhole. Put your soul in a K hole.¬†\n\n**Find the hole that speaks to you.**\n\nüï≥Ô∏è Our **BASE HOLE**: we‚Äôll build 4 fully-formed, hand-crafted infinity holes ‚Äî weird, sparkly, and ready to be found.  \nüåà Our **STRETCHED HOLE**: we‚Äôll expand to 8 immersive, LED-lit portals complete with scavenger clues and Hole Passports.  \nüåÄ Our STRECH of A Stretched Hole (aka **THE GAPING HOLE**): we‚Äôll add weatherproofing, possibly sound, and a level of extra that no one asked for‚Ä¶ but everyone deserves.",
